
  Maintain full set of accounts as well as verify and approve AP, AR, GL journals;
  Ensure accuracy and completeness of accounts
  Prepare monthly financial reports and schedules for management
  Provide support to operation team
  Ensure all cash and banking transactions are accurate, complete and authorised
  Ensure all internal controls are adhered to and intact
  Propose new controls and process to improve efficiency
  Reconcile bank statements in timely manner
  Follow up on outstanding debts and ensure credit limits are properly set up
